text: Primax Broadcasting Network is a broadcast radio network in the Philippines. Its main office is located at 10th Floor, Jacinta Bldg. II, EDSA, Makati City. The network is owned by the Yabut family (original owners of Nation Broadcasting Corporation prior to 1998).Republic Act No. 8134KBP Members MemoRieS FM is Primax's FM network of stations in Baguio and Cebu.
